Directions to run the python script
To run the python script,run the following command in the terminal:

> python3 hw4.py

As requested by the instructions, the comamnd will reproduce the dev1.out and dev2.out ﬁles.

The ﬁles will be located in the following directories:

1. The train, test and dev ﬁles will be located in the data folder as was provided by the hw.
2. The glove embeddings will be located in the working directory as glove.6B.100d.gz

The following are the dependencies required for the py ﬁle,

- pandas
- torch
- from torch import nn
- numpy
- from torch.utils.data import DataLoader,Dataset
- from sklearn.utils.class_weight import compute_class_weight
- from torch.optim.lr_scheduler import CosineAnnealingLR, ReduceLROnPlateau
- from tqdm import tqdm
- from sklearn.metrics import classiﬁcation_report
- import gzip

